\c 43
\s Abafowabo bakaJosefa babuyela eGibithe loBenjamini
\p
\v 1 Indlala-ke yayinzima\x + 41.54,57.\x* elizweni.
\v 2 Kwasekusithi sebeqedile ukudla ababebuye lakho eGibithe, uyise wathi kubo: Buyelani, lisithengele ukudla okulutshwana.
\v 3 UJuda wasekhuluma kuye wathi: Leyondoda yasiqonqosela\f + \fk yasiqonqosela: \fl Heb. \fq yafakaza lokufakaza.\f* yathi: Kalisoze libubone ubuso bami ngaphandle kokuthi umnawenu lilaye\x + 42.20; 44.23.\x*.
\v 4 Uba uthuma umnawethu lathi, sizakwehla siyekuthengela ukudla,
\v 5 kodwa uba unga\add m\add*thumi, kasiyikwehla, ngoba leyondoda yathi kithi: Kalisoze libubone ubuso bami ngaphandle kokuthi umnawenu lilaye.
\v 6 UIsrayeli wasesithi: Lenzelani okubi kimi ngokuyazisa leyondoda ukuthi liselomnawenu?
\v 7 Basebesithi: Leyondoda yabuzisisa\f + \fk yabuzisisa: \fl Heb. \fq yabuza lokubuza.\f* mayelana lathi langezihlobo zethu, isithi: Uyihlo usaphila yini? Lilomnawenu yini? Sayilandisela ngalawomazwi\f + \fk ngalawo-: \fl Heb. \fq umlomo.\f*; ukwazi sasikwazi yini ukuthi izakuthi: Yehlani lomnawenu?
\v 8 UJuda wasesithi kuIsrayeli uyise: Thuma umfana lami; besesisukuma sihambe, ukuze siphile singafi\x + 42.2.\x*, lathi, lawe, labantwanyana bethu.
\v 9 Mina ngizakuba yisibambiso sakhe; uzambiza esandleni sami; uba ngingambuyisi kuwe ngimbeke phambi kwakho, ngizakuba lecala kuwe zonke insuku\x + 44.32.\x*.
\v 10 Isibili uba besingalibalanga, qotho ngabe khathesi sesibuyile kabili.
\v 11 UIsrayeli uyise wasesithi kubo: Uba kunjalo khathesi, yenzani lokhu; thathani okwezithelo ezikhethiweyo zelizwe ezitsheni zenu, liyehlisele leyondoda isipho, inhlaka eyingcosana\x + 37.25.\x*, loluju oluyingcosana, isinongo, lemure*, imkelu yepistakiyo, lama-alimondi;
\v 12 lithathe imali iphindwe kabili esandleni senu; futhi imali eyabuyiselwayo emlonyeni wamasaka enu\x + 42.25,27,35.\x* liyibuyisele esandleni senu, mhlawumbe kwaba yisiphosiso.
\v 13 Lithathe futhi umfowenu, lisukume, libuyele kuleyondoda.
\v 14 UNkulunkulu uSomandla\x + 17.1.\x* kaliphe isihawu phambi kwaleyondoda, ukuze alikhululele omunye umfowenu loBenjamini. Mina-ke, uba ngemukwa abantwana, ngiyemukwa.
\p
\v 15 Amadoda asethatha lesosipho, athatha imali ephindwe kabili esandleni sawo loBenjamini; asukuma ehlela eGibithe, ema phambi kukaJosefa.
\v 16 Kwathi uJosefa embona uBenjamini elabo, wathi kumphathi wendlu yakhe\x + 43.19; 24.2; 39.4; 44.1,4.\x*: Ngenisa lamadoda endlini, uhlabe isifuyo, ulungise, ngoba lamadoda azakudla lami emini.
\v 17 Indoda yenza njengoba uJosefa etshilo, lendoda yawangenisa amadoda endlini kaJosefa.
\v 18 Amadoda asesesaba, ngoba engeniswe endlini kaJosefa; athi: Singenisiwe ngenxa yemali eyabuyiselwa emasakeni ethu kuqala, ukuze asijume\f + \fk asijume: \fl Heb. \fq azigiqe phezu kwethu.\f* ehlele phezu kwethu, asithathe sibe yizigqili, labobabhemi bethu.
\v 19 Asesondela endodeni eyayingumphathi wendlu kaJosefa, akhuluma kuyo emnyango wendlu,
\v 20 athi: Mayuyu nkosi yami! Sehla lokwehla kuqala ukuthenga ukudla\x + 42.3,10.\x*.
\v 21 Kwasekusithi sesifike endlini yezihambi, savula amasaka ethu, khangela-ke, imali yalowo lalowo yayisemlonyeni wesaka lakhe\x + 42.27.\x*, imali yethu ngesisindo sayo; siyibuyisile esandleni sethu.
\v 22 Lenye imali sehlelayo esandleni sethu, ukuthenga ukudla. Kasazi ukuthi ngubani ofake imali yethu emasakeni ethu.
\v 23 Wasesithi: Ukuthula kakube kini, lingesabi. UNkulunkulu wenu loNkulunkulu kayihlo ulinikile inotho emasakeni enu. Imali yenu yeza kimi. Wasemkhuphela kubo uSimeyoni.
\v 24 Indoda yasiwangenisa amadoda endlini kaJosefa, ya\add wa\add*nika amanzi; asegeza inyawo zawo; yasinika obabhemi bawo ukudla\x + 18.4; 19.2; 24.32.\x*.
\v 25 Aselungisa isipho\x + 43.11.\x* waze wafika uJosefa emini, ngoba ayezwile ukuthi bazakudla isinkwa lapho.
\p
\v 26 Kwathi uJosefa esefikile endlini, amlethela endlini isipho esasisesandleni sawo, amkhothamela emhlabathini\x + 43.28; 37.7,9,10; 42.6.\x*.
\v 27 Wasewabuza impilo wathi: Uyaphila uyihlo yini, ixhegu elalikhuluma ngalo? Lisaphila yini\x + 42.11,13.\x*?
\v 28 Asesithi: Inceku yakho ubaba isekhona, isaphila. Asekhothamela phansi amkhonza.
\v 29 Wasephakamisa amehlo akhe, wabona uBenjamini umfowabo, indodana kanina\x + 35.18.\x*, wathi: Nguye lo umnawenu omncinyane yini elakhuluma ngaye kimi\x + 42.13.\x*? Wathi futhi: UNkulunkulu kabe lomusa kuwe, ndodana yami.
\v 30 UJosefa wasephangisa, ngoba imibilini yakhe yatshisekela umfowabo\x + 1 Kho. 3.26. Hos. 11.8.\x*; wadinga \add indawo\add* yokukhala inyembezi; wangena ekamelweni eliphakathi, wakhala inyembezi khona\x + 42.24.\x*.
\v 31 Esegezile ubuso bakhe, waphuma; esezibambile\x + 45.1.\x* wathi: Fakani isinkwa.
\v 32 Bamfakela yedwa, lawo wodwa, lamaGibithe, ayesidla laye, wodwa, ngoba amaGibithe ayengedle isinkwa lamaHeberu, ngoba lokho kwakuyisinengiso kumaGibithe\x + 46.34. Eks. 8.26.\x*.
\v 33 Asehlala phambi kwakhe, izibulo njengobuzibulo balo, lecinathunjana njengobucinathunjana balo; lamadoda amangala enye kwenye.
\v 34 Wasewabela kulokhu okwakuphambi kwakhe\x + 2 Sam. 11.8.\x*; kodwa isabelo sikaBenjamini saphindwa kahlanu\x + 45.22.\x* okwedlula isabelo sawo wonke. Asenatha athokoza laye.
